From: STGR Browser Team <dev@stgr-browser.dev>
Date: Mon, 1 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: Remove all Mozilla telemetry, studies, and experiments

Removes:
- Telemetry reporting infrastructure
- Firefox Shield studies
- Normandy experiments
- Crash reporting
- Usage statistics
- Performance monitoring pings
- All background data collection
- Telemetry related build flags and modules

